data.description: This 1040 sq. ft. home is a diamond in the rough, awaiting your personal touch and creativity to transform it into your dream haven. Located close to westside amenities, this property offers the perfect balance of convenience and potential. As you step inside, you'll notice the endless possibilities this home presents. While it may need some tender loving care (TLC), it provides an excellent canvas for renovation and customization, allowing you to tailor it to your unique preferences and style. The main living area encompasses an open layout, providing a versatile space for you to design and organize to suit your lifestyle. With a little vision, the living and dining spaces can be transformed into cozy and inviting areas for entertaining guests or spending quality time with family. The kitchen, although in need of updates, is a functional space with the potential to become the heart of the home. You have the opportunity to bring in modern appliances, stylish cabinetry, and countertops, creating a culinary haven that will inspire your cooking endeavors. With three bedrooms and two bathrooms, this home has the capacity to accommodate a growing family or provide additional space for a home office or hobby room. The bedrooms offer a quiet retreat after a long day, and the bathrooms can be redesigned to incorporate contemporary fixtures and finishes. One significant advantage of this property is the new HVAC system, ensuring that you'll have efficient heating and cooling throughout the year, providing comfort and peace of mind. The backyard presents a blank canvas for landscaping and outdoor improvements. You can design your own oasis, whether it's a lush garden, a tranquil patio, or a play area for people & pets. Beyond the property's boundaries, you'll find a wealth of westside amenities just a stone's throw away. From shopping centers, restaurants, parks, and recreational facilities, everything you need is within easy reach, enhancing the convenience and appeal of the location. This home offers an exciting opportunity for those with a vision and passion for renovation. With its prime location and new HVAC system, it's a diamond in the rough that, with a little TLC, can shine brilliantly as your ideal home. Don't miss the chance to turn this house into your dream home!
